Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.45,0:23:45.42,Captions,,0000,0000,0000,,Executive Producer\NHENRY GOTO
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.49,0:23:47.45,Captions,,0000,0000,0000,,Producers\NSATOSHI FUJII, REIKO MATSUO\N& JONATHAN KLEIN
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.52,0:23:49.49,Captions,,0000,0000,0000,,Subtitlers\NBRETT JACOBSEN, DIANA TOLIN,\NAKI MATSUMOTO & MAKOTO SHIRAI
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.76,0:24:00.93,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor Moriarty has discovered\Nthe route used to transport cash...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.40,0:24:03.53,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,by horse and carriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.74,0:24:07.17,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,He's set up traps all over the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.87,0:24:10.10,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,Can Holmes stop him in time?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.58,0:24:16.31,Behind the Scenes,,0000,0000,0000,,If you find yourself in a mystery,\Nplease come see us at Baker Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.32,0:24:21.85,Ep Title,,0000,0000,0000,,The Professor's Big\NFailure in the Storm!!
